<p>As a part of the last rites, a prayer meet for <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/karisma-kapoors-ex-husband-sunjay-kapurs-4-day-old-post-says-your-time-on-earth-is-limited-1391325">Sunjay Kapur</a> is scheduled to take place on June 22. On June 18, the family shared a note giving information about the prayer meeting planned for the billionaire. This meet will be taking place in Delhi at the Taj Hotel.&nbsp;</p>

<h3><strong>Reason for Sunjay Kapur&#39;s demise</strong></h3>

<p><a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/are-karisma-kapoors-kids-getting-a-share-of-sunjay-kapurs-wealth-find-out-who-might-take-over-his-rs-31000-crore-business-empire-1391504">Sunjay Kapur</a> was a polo player and the chairman of Sona Comstar, a company specialising in the manufacture of parts for electric vehicles. He passed away on June 16 in England after he suffered a fatal heart attack during a polo match.</p>

<p>According to reports, it is known that <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/sunjay-kapurs-pic-from-his-last-polo-semi-final-match-goes-viral-as-businessmans-team-heads-for-finals-1391542">Sunjay Kapur</a> accidentally swallowed a bee while he was playing Polo. This triggered an allergic reaction inside his body which ultimately lead to a heart attack. He is now survived by his wife, Priya Sachdev, son Azarius, stepdaughter Safira Chatwal, Samaira Kapoor, and Kiaan Kapoor.&nbsp;</p>

