<p><strong>1. Gagan Arora</strong> - Gagan Arora, best known for his roles in shows like College Romance and SonyLIV series Tabbar, is seen in a&nbsp;lead role as Rohan. His role of being stubborn yet madly in love will tickle your funny bones and make you emotional. His romantic life is shaken by money troubles, adding emotional complexity to the narrative.</p>

