<p>In an interview with Vishal Malhotra, well-known paparazzo Manav Manglani opened up on Katrina Kaif and Vicky Kaushal&rsquo;s first spotting after attending producer Amritpal Singh Bindra&rsquo;s Diwali party. He shared that the moment was entirely unplanned.</p>

