<p>He recalled that as the duo were trying to locate their cars, his team happened to spot them. It was only when they noticed the cameras that they realized they&#39;d been captured together for the first time in public. &ldquo;That&rsquo;s when it hit them; they had been seen together publicly for the first time. That photo went viral, and how,&rdquo; the paparazzo shared.</p>

