<p>&quot;I have been acting for 38 years now. And I have at least 200 relatives. Mai to ek ko bhi nahin karva paaya...dekhiye blessings apni apni.. mehnat apni hai (I haven&#39;t been able to get them work here. It is blessings, hard work), and finally it is the audience who decides,&quot; he further added.</p>

