<p>Directed by Tarun Mansukhani, Housefull 5 promises the return of the franchise&rsquo;s signature blend of over-the-top comedy and lavish visuals and is scheduled to hit theaters on June 6.</p>

<p>The first&nbsp;Housefull&nbsp;movie, directed by Sajid Khan, was released in 2010. It features Akshay Kumar alongside Jiah Khan, Arjun Rampal, Jacqueline Fernandez, Lara Dutta and Chunky Panday. The sequel, also directed by Sajid Khan, came out in 2012, followed by Sajid-Farhad-helmed&nbsp;Housefull 3&nbsp;in 2016 and Farhad Samji&rsquo;s&nbsp;Housefull 4&nbsp;in 2019.</p>
